{"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"languages":["swift"],"platforms":["macOS"],"tokens":[{"kind":"attribute","text":"nonisolated"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"transaction"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"value"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"some"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:SQ","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"Equatable"},{"kind":"text","text":", "},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"_"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"transform"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"@escaping"},{"kind":"text","text":" ("},{"kind":"keyword","text":"inout"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:15OpenSwiftUICore11TransactionV","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"Transaction","identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/Transaction"},{"kind":"text","text":") -> "},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:s4Voida","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"Void"},{"kind":"text","text":") -> "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"some"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:15OpenSwiftUICore4ViewP","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"View","identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/View"},{"kind":"text","text":"\n"}]}]},{"kind":"parameters","parameters":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"A value to monitor for changes."}]}],"name":"value"},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The transformation to apply to transactions","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"within this view.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"name":"transform"}]},{"content":[{"level":2,"text":"Return Value","type":"heading","anchor":"return-value"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"A view that wraps this view and applies a transformation to"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"all transactions used within the view whenever "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"value"},{"type":"text","text":" changes."}],"type":"paragraph"}],"kind":"content"},{"content":[{"type":"heading","text":"Discussion","level":2,"anchor":"discussion"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Use this modifier to change or replace the animation used in a view."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Consider three identical views controlled by a"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"button that changes all three simultaneously:"}]},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The first view animates rotating the “Rotation” ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/Text","type":"reference"},{"text":" view by 360","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"degrees.","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The second uses the ","type":"text"},{"code":"transaction(_:)","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" modifier to change the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"animation by adding a delay to the start of the animation","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"by two seconds and then increases the rotational speed of the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"“Rotation\\nModified” ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/Text","type":"reference"},{"text":" view animation by a factor of 2.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The third uses the ","type":"text"},{"code":"transaction(_:)","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" modifier to disable animations","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"affecting the “Animation\\nReplaced” ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/Text","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"text":" view.","type":"text"}]}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The following code implements these animations:","type":"text"}]},{"type":"codeListing","code":["struct TransactionExample: View {","    @State var flag = false","","    var body: some View {","        VStack(spacing: 50) {","            HStack(spacing: 30) {","                Text(\"Rotation\")","                    .rotationEffect(Angle(degrees: flag ? 360 : 0))","","                Text(\"Rotation\\nModified\")","                    .rotationEffect(Angle(degrees: flag ? 360 : 0))","                    .transaction(value: flag) { t in","                        t.animation =","                            t.animation?.delay(2.0).speed(2)","                    }","","                Text(\"Animation\\nReplaced\")","                    .rotationEffect(Angle(degrees: flag ? 360 : 0))","                    .transaction(value: flag) { t in","                        t.disableAnimations = true","                    }","            }","","            Button(\"Animate\") {","                withAnimation(.easeIn(duration: 2.0)) {","                    flag.toggle()","                }","            }","        }","    }","}"],"syntax":"swift"}],"kind":"content"}],"kind":"symbol","hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI","doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/VStack"]]},"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/VStack\/transaction(value:_:)"},"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"major":0,"minor":3},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Applies the given transaction mutation function to all animations used"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"within the view."}],"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/openswiftui\/vstack\/transaction(value:_:)"]}],"metadata":{"modules":[{"relatedModules":["OpenSwiftUICore"],"name":"OpenSwiftUI"}],"externalID":"s:15OpenSwiftUICore4ViewPAAE11transa